  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <h3><strong>Makes Extracting Ancient Debris Simpler And Faster.</strong></h3>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/white-netheriite\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5267ff7a4de63cacf0d3520d0ab27fdc58865810.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"CurseForge project page\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/white-netherite\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/be27fc74ec25823c7ae6c0205038b3d419f4d7b3.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"Modrinth project page\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/white-netherite-6837460/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/40e6888d1cdef25608cef172d1e9ca76ae61e3f2.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft page\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/azuhkai\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/399fbe8c7eecab1fb193f2f0ee0d2af8472ac508.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"Support on Ko-fi\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/dU8SfBeb3N\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f6cbe6e30f50da94aff2eb76fdb68c440eb46c7.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"Join our Discord server\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://x.com/azuhkai\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2d964a5355acf10ab912daf63f64a527bd7132e1.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"AzuhWorks on X\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://patreon.com/azuhkai\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c9c702e258e57b1d5f308db216f78a3b5126c6e3.png\" width=\"60\" alt=\"Support on Patreon\"/>\n  </a>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n![Ancient debris visibility comparison](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/49ff0470057bfdc95027aecd65bf654524762040.jpeg)\n\n\n### Features\n- Improved visibility of ancient debris in low-light environments.\n- Ancient debris now uses a lighter and brighter color.\n- Makes netherite easier to find while mining.\n\n---\n\nThis resource pack improves the visibility of ancient debris by using a lighter and brighter color.\nIt is designed to make netherite mining easier, especially in low-light environments such as the Nether.\nNo gameplay mechanics are changed — only the visuals are enhanced.\n",
